{"id":5713,"date":"2014-10-31T09:13:54","date_gmt":"2014-10-31T08:13:54","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/?p=5713"},"modified":"2014-10-31T09:17:47","modified_gmt":"2014-10-31T08:17:47","slug":"tpi-awards-favourite-international-caterer-nomination","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/tpi-awards-favourite-international-caterer-nomination\/","title":{"rendered":"TPI Awards &#8211; Favourite International Caterer Nomination &#8211; Red Radish"},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Red Radish<\/strong> were absolutely delighted to find out that we have been nominated for an award recognising the production industries\u2019 favourite catering company. OK, at this point it might only be a <a title=\"TPi Awards\" href=\"http:\/\/www.tpiawards.com\/votenow\/index.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>TPi Awards nomination<\/strong><\/a> but to be included in a list alongside established touring catering companies such as Eat to the Beat, Eatopia and North American favourite Spectrum Catering is a great accolade in itself. It remains to be seen how the voting will go and if last year\u2019s winner and well known tour caterer Popcorn will triumph again but whatever happens we are chuffed to be on that list.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/10\/Untitled.png\" class=\"pretty_image\" data-rel=\"prettyPhoto[5713]\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-5717\" src=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/10\/Untitled.png\" alt=\"TPI Awards Favourite Catering Company Red Radish\" width=\"1986\" height=\"1054\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/10\/Untitled.png 1986w, https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/10\/Untitled-600x318.png 600w, https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/10\/Untitled-300x159.png 300w, https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/10\/Untitled-1024x543.png 1024w, https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/10\/Untitled-436x231.png 436w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1986px) 100vw, 1986px\" \/><\/a>The <a title=\"TPi Magazine\" href=\"http:\/\/tpimagazine.com\/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Total Production Industry Magazine<\/strong><\/a> (TPi) Awards were set up in 2002 to recognise designers, engineers, companies and individuals who have made an impact in the world of concert touring.\u00a0Obviously anyone who has ever worked on a tour will know just how important catering can be and how it can totally carry a hardworking team through. Just ask the Dralion and <a title=\"Quidam on Facebook\" href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/Quidam?fref=ts\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Quidam<\/strong><\/a> tours of <a title=\"Cirque du Soleil\" href=\"http:\/\/www.cirquedusoleil.com\/en\/home\/shows.aspx\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Cirque du Soleil<\/strong><\/a>\u00a0 (also nominated in lots of categories) who Red Radish have been working with all over Europe since winning their super-prestigious catering contract last summer.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/10\/1523191_10152069729501226_311678095_o.jpg\" class=\"pretty_image\" data-rel=\"prettyPhoto[5713]\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-5725\" src=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/10\/1523191_10152069729501226_311678095_o.jpg\" alt=\"Louise Bird - Chef at Red Radish\" width=\"1022\" height=\"1110\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/10\/1523191_10152069729501226_311678095_o.jpg 1022w, https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/10\/1523191_10152069729501226_311678095_o-600x652.jpg 600w, https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/10\/1523191_10152069729501226_311678095_o-276x300.jpg 276w, https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/10\/1523191_10152069729501226_311678095_o-942x1024.jpg 942w, https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/10\/1523191_10152069729501226_311678095_o-284x309.jpg 284w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1022px) 100vw, 1022px\" \/><\/a>Now in its 14th consecutive year the TPi winners, (as voted for by the industry) will be held at Battersea Evolution in London <strong>on 16 February 2015 when over <\/strong>1000 people from all corners of the live music business, the TPi Awards acknowledges and rewards the achievements of the most <strong>talented and successful individuals<\/strong> and service companies working within the industry.<\/p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/mondialepublishing.wufoo.com\/forms\/tpi-awards-voting-2015\/\" target=\"_blank\">It would be great if you could please find two minutes to vote for us and our wonderful clients Cirque du Soleil<\/a><\/strong><\/p>\n<p><strong>Timetable:<\/strong><\/p>\n<table width=\"395\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"215\"><strong>Call for entries:\u00a0<\/strong><\/td>\n<td width=\"155\"><strong>September 1<\/strong><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Voting Ends<\/strong><\/td>\n<td><strong>October 31<\/strong><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Shortlist announced:<\/strong><\/td>\n<td><strong>November 7<\/strong><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Winners announced at awards:<\/strong><\/td>\n<td><strong>February 16<\/strong><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p><strong>For further information about the event please contact:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><strong>Amy Wright<\/strong><br \/>\nTel: +44 (0) 161 476 8360<br \/>\nEmail:\u00a0<a href=\"mailto:a.wright@mondiale.co.uk\">a.wright@mondiale.co.uk<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Red Radish were absolutely delighted to find out that we have been nominated for an award recognising the production industries\u2019 favourite catering company. OK, at this point it might only&#8230; <a class=\"more-